race.comment: BRUTE FORCE (3) is a well performed dog who recorded his 7th career win last time out at this track (28.03). Yet to taste defeat from two runs out of this box. Expected to measure up again. GALENTO (5) could manage only second last time but ran useful time (28.02) at this track over 500m when beaten 1.5 lengths in a Grade 5 H. This is tougher but looks a leading chance again. KEY PHILOSOPHY (7) ran the fastest on the card last time scoring by 1.5 lengths (27.93) at this track. Form should stack up again here. SLICK BADGER (2) racing over this distance brings the best out in him.
